## Required Behavior

- Always read `docs/frontend/` before creating new components or styling patterns.
- Reuse existing frontend components and established modal/form patterns.
- Keep styles and interaction patterns consistent with the documented guidelines.
- Avoid introducing new one-off styling where shared components already exist.
- When in doubt, check the existing UI primitives in `components/ui/` and domain components in `components/field/` before writing new code.
